name: Jake's Fantastic Space Adventure
description:
JFSA (Jake’s Fantastic Space Adventure) is an arcade style space shooter game with a twist!

JFSA was made using the LOVE2D framework: https://love2d.org/

The music was made in Musagi: http://www.drpetter.se/project_musagi.html

Leaderboard
The high score leaderboard can be found here: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BFu5KLRDlIobk54SnSOymoh7Cd2JvJIuRmIdFrvPzUI/edit?usp=sharing

High score submission instructions are on the leaderboard.
